External media
Strictly necessary cookies
Strictly necessary or functional cookies relate to the functionality of our website and enable us to improve the service we offer you via our website. For example, these cookies allow us to transmit information across several pages of our website. They ensure that you can visit our website again without having to re-enter your information.
Enabled
Performance cookies
Performance cookies enable us to:
Recognise and count the number of visitors to our website
Observe and record the user behaviour of our visitors
This allows us to see how frequently certain pages and content are visited and which areas of our website are most popular. In addition, it means that we can improve the service offered based on users’ interests.
Enabled
External media
Content from video and social media platforms is blocked by default. If cookies for external media are accepted, no separate consent is required to access this content.
